["The best way to stop Lissandra from moving using her Glacial Path is to immobilize her before she reactivates it.","Lissandra's Ring of Frost has a long cooldown at early ranks; engage her while it's on cooldown.","Lissandra's Ice Shard only slows the first unit it hits. Approach Lissandra from behind your team's minions to avoid being slowed."]
